Package: filemanager-actions
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: ksh,
            filemanager-actions-nautilus-extension,
            filemanager-actions-caja-extension,
            filemanager-actions-nemo-extension
Description: filemanager extension to configure programs to launch
 Filemanager actions is an extension for the GNOME file manager.
 It allows the configuration of programs to be launched on files selected
 in the selected interface.

